    "description": "Fast, fiery and full of goodness, this charred aubergine is spiked with soy, sambal and heaps of aromats. Finish with lemongrass, Thai basil and lime leaf for a fragrant stir-fry that's ready in minutes and gone in seconds. Serve with Tenderstem Broccoli to the side.",
